data.description: This property cannot be shown until Friday, October 6th.  Escape the hustle and bustle and embrace the peaceful countryside in this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, nestled on a generous 2.5-acre lot. With a detached two-car garage and a greenhouse, this property is a haven for those seeking serenity and a connection to nature.  Step inside to discover a cozy and inviting living space that welcomes you with open arms. The home boasts newer windows that flood the interior with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.  A new roof installed in 2021 ensures that you can enjoy worry-free living for years to come, while the recently upgraded sump pump provides added peace of mind during rainy seasons.  Your comfort is a top priority with the installation of a new furnace, AC, and heat pump in 2023. This means you'll stay cozy in the winter and cool in the summer, no matter what the weather brings.,The property provides ample space for outdoor activities and hobbies. Cultivate your green thumb in the HUGE greenhouse, perfect for nurturing plants and flowers throughout the year.  Your vehicles and equipment will find a secure home in the detached two-car garage and storage shed, offering plenty of room for storage and projects.  Rest easy knowing that the conventional septic system was last pumped in August 2023, with no issues noted.  Embrace the tranquility of country living while still enjoying the convenience of being just a short drive away from essential amenities and local attractions.  This countryside retreat offers a simple and serene way of life, where the beauty of nature is your backdrop, and the comforts of home surround you. Don't miss this opportunity to make this property your own piece of paradise.  Information contained herein must be verified by user/buyer. This information is compiled from miscellaneous sources and is believed accurate but not warranted. Neither the listing broker nor its agents or property owner are responsible for the accuracy of the information. Buyers are advised to verify all information. Electronic earnest money through TrustFunds is now available.TrustFunds will charge a $5 convenience fee to the buyer for the use of this service.
